⬇️FULL RECIPE⬇️

150 calories 30g protein (for the entire pint)

Vanilla Protein Soft Serve

Original recipe from my E-Book
Check out the link in my bio for my Creami E-Book with over 100 recipes like this one!

- 1 @drinknurri Vanilla Protein Shake
- 20-25g (2 tbsp) sugar substitute (I like Monk Fruit sweetener)
- 2.5g (½ tsp) vanilla bean paste (or extract)
- 1g (¼ tsp) salt
- 1g (¼ tsp) xanthan gum
150 cal 2g C, 2.5g F, 30g P

Instructions:
1. Blend all ingredients for the base and freeze (at least 16 hours)
2. Run under hot water for at least 60 seconds
3. Spin on “Lite Ice Cream” setting
4. Spin on “Respin” setting
5. Respin again if powdery
